lead_paragraph: Rafael Esquivel, a former president of Venezuela’s soccer federation who had been detained since May, was to appear in federal court in Brooklyn.

headline.print_headline: Swiss Extradite FIFA Bribery Case Suspect Esquivel to US
headline.main: Swiss Extradite Venezuelan Soccer Official to U.S.
